{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f1e2d3c4-b5a6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "TariffShield API",
    "description": "## TariffShield API\n\nSoroban-backed customs-bond collateral rail for US importers.\n\n### How to import\n\n1. In Postman, click **Import** and select this file.\n2. Import the companion `tariff-shield.postman_environment.json` under **Environments**.\n3. Select the **TariffShield** environment from the environment picker.\n4. Fill in `importer_email` / `importer_password` (or `admin_email` / `admin_password`) with real credentials.\n\n### Auto-authentication\n\nThe collection pre-request script automatically calls `POST /auth/login` on the first request and stores the returned JWT in the `jwt_token` collection variable. Subsequent requests reuse that token. To force a fresh login, clear the `jwt_token` collection variable.\n\n### Running the full importer flow\n\n1. **Auth › Sign Up** — create a new importer account.\n2. **Auth › Login** — obtain a JWT (auto-done by pre-request script on other requests).\n3. **Importers › Create Importer** — register the importer on-chain and receive `importer_id`; copy it into the environment.\n4. **Importers › Upload Tariff CSV** — submit HTS line items to compute required collateral.\n5. **Importers › Deposit Collateral** — fund the importer's collateral bucket.\n6. **Importers › Get Importer** — verify on-chain balance matches expected collateral.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "var token = pm.collectionVariables.get('jwt_token');",
          "if (!token) {",
          "  var baseUrl = pm.environment.get('base_url');",
          "  var email = pm.environment.get('importer_email');",
          "  var password = pm.environment.get('importer_password');",
          "  pm.sendRequest({",
          "    url: baseUrl + '/auth/login',",
          "    method: 'POST',",
          "    header: [{ key: 'Content-Type', value: 'application/json' }],",
          "    body: {",
          "      mode: 'raw',",
          "      raw: JSON.stringify({ email: email, password: password })",
          "    }",
          "  }, function(err, res) {",
          "    if (!err && res.code === 200) {",
          "      pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.json().token);",
          "    }",
          "  });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "JWT bearer token — auto-populated by the collection pre-request script on first request. Clear this variable to force re-authentication."
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign Up",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
